## 🧠 What You Just Learned

| Concept | Tag | What it does |
|---|---|---|
| Page structure | `html, head, body` | Skeleton of every webpage |
| Headings | `h1, h2, h3` | Titles — h1 is biggest |
| Paragraph | `p` | Normal text |
| Link | `a href=""` | Clickable link |
| List | `ul, li` | Navigation menus |
| Section | `section` | Groups a page section |
| Container | `div` | Groups any elements |
| Navigation | `nav` | Top navbar |
| Footer | `footer` | Bottom of page |
| class | `class=""` | Names elements for CSS styling |
| id | `id=""` | Unique name — used for jump links |

